---
Source:
  - Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
    ISBN: 978-1571746931
Author: Kahlil Gibran
Page: 156
---
God leaned over me and
whispered sweet words in my ear.
He embraced me like the sea embraces
the stream that rushes to her.
When I found myself down in the valley,
God was also there.
